flowchart LR
    Insured[Insured]
    Agent[Agent / Broker]
    Insurer[Insurer]
    Reinsurer[Reinsurer]
    ReBroker[Reinsurance Broker]
    Claimant[Claimant<br/>can be insured or third party]
    Invest[Investment Portfolio]
    Reg[State / Tax Authority]

    Insured -->|Gross Premium| Agent
    Agent -->|Net of commission| Insurer
    Agent -.Commission 10-25%.-> Agent

    Insurer -->|Premium taxes| Reg
    Insurer -->|Ceded premium| ReBroker
    ReBroker -->|Net of brokerage| Reinsurer
    ReBroker -.Ceding commission.-> Insurer
    ReBroker -.Brokerage fee.-> ReBroker

    Insurer -->|Reserve / Float| Invest
    Invest -.Investment income.-> Insurer

    Insurer -->|Claim payment| Claimant
    Reinsurer -->|Reinsurance recovery<br/>to primary insurer| Insurer
    Insurer -.Retention kept.-> Insurer

    Insurer -->|Profit commission<br/>if applicable| Agent

